{"id": "1352436494454755441", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 19, "author_id": "1209714639508611072", "author_name": "alfarro09", "author_bot": false, "content": "Imagine being her, an EoS game character got a second chance just to say goodbye to the former players of her game and disappeared right away.\n\nThe thing that makes it sadder is because she's aware that her Game is EoS and she didn't really want it. <:flop:1236937860922343466>", "timestamp": "2025-03-21T00:19:47.333000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-03-21T00:21:08.429000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["856452553083584512"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1352329664583958589", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
